==Swedish==

===Noun===
'''förkläde'''

#[[apron]]; An article of [[clothing]] worn over the front of the [[torso]] for protection from spills.
# {{obsolete}} A person who follows, and is supposed to protect the [[honour]] of a young [[woman]] when meeting [[men]].

